    "cover": "https://drewprototypes.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/drew-waters-music.com/album_images/humbolt_detroit_vol_01.png",
    "notes": "recording close to the intersection of humboldt and detroit streets, this collection represents a conversation that begins but never quite concludes-  short gestures offered, responses, shaped by some assumptions. this release is the first in an ongoing series of experiments, exploring a prompt, some space, and a quick decision —what can happen when one listens and carefully responds..",
    "credits": "\n        <div class=\"dw-credits-title\">credits</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">drew waters · guitar, recording, production</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">caitlin moss · drums, recording</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">recorded in los angeles 1 jan 2026</div>\n      ",
