    "notes": "\nbuilt almost entirely from hardware limitations and repetition.\n\n<br>\n\nthe tr606 handles rhythm duties while the tb303 and sh101 generate most harmonic and melodic material. some OP1 textures and resampling pushed things into a more unstable direction.\n\n<br>\n\na lot of these tracks began as long-form jams recorded directly into pro tools, then reduced into shorter structures later. minimal editing, minimal correction, mostly live manipulation.\n\n<br>\n\nrecorded in los angeles, june 2025.\n",
    "credits": "\n        <div class=\"dw-credits-title\">credits</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">drew waters · tr606, tb303, sh101, OP1</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">recorded in los angeles, june 2025</div>\n      ",
