  "notes": "different-ish direction, similar components and references. no synths were harmed or used in the making of this production. all sounds derived from my guitar/bass and a series of pedals and routing. the mere messing with the adsr of a transient creates synth-like attacks. something that i'll love until I die. add some stutters, reverbs, lo-fi eq, some simple repetitive drum grooves, barely any melody and patience...",
