  {
  "id": "rock_for_bass_and_drums_volume_3",
  "title": "rock for bass and drums: volume 3",
  "year": "2019",
  "cover": "https://drewprototypes.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/drew-waters-music.com/album_images/rock%20for%20bass%20and%20drums%20cover.png",
  "notes": "<div><strong>big time buck white</strong> someone told me about a person who goes by this name. for weeks i could not get it out of my head. i'm told the person has a world built around this persona.</div><br><div><strong>sara's latte</strong> when i first moved to the east bay, i gravitated to a coffee shop that made killin' soy lattes. the best were made by a very cool person named sara. sadly for me she doesn't make them anymore.</div><br><div><strong>aikenaut</strong> this was written for my old friend matt aiken. i think this is just one perspective of one aspect of matt's personality.</div><br><div><strong>orange targa</strong> as a kid watching american television, including abc after school specials, i always assumed that everyone in california drove orange targas.</div><br><div><strong>ziva blooms</strong> this was written for a little person i have not yet met, and i hope to meet real soon.</div><br><div><strong>shiny red ten</strong></div><br><div><strong>mericana</strong> this is a reflection of how i perceive aspects of american culture.</div>",
  "credits": "\n        <div class=\"dw-credits-title\">credits</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">released january 1, 2019</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">drew waters · bass, sounds, compositions, recording engineering</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">alex vittum · drums</div>\n      ",
